Error:

./boost/python/detail/wrap_python.hpp:57:11: fatal error: pyconfig.h: No such file or directory
   57 | # include <pyconfig.h>

Solution:
 a) Using apt: sudo apt-get install python-dev
 b) Using local files: export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:/path/to/folder/where/pyconfig.h/resides"

